{"id": "art-2461", "label": "Art. 2461", "title": "Art. 2461", "slug": "art-2461", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1232341522\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1766\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1232341522\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 246<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1114543557\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1765\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1114543557\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cazul unei\nfuziuni prin <span class=SpellE>absorb&#355;ie</span> prin care una sau mai\nmulte <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> sunt dizolvate\nf&#259;r&#259; a intra în lichidare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> transfer&#259;\ntoate activele <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivele lor unei alte <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> care <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span>\ntoate <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span> lor sau alte titluri conferind\ndrepturi de vot în adunarea general&#259;, aprobarea fuziunii de c&#259;tre\nadunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> implicate în fuziune, în <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> art. 239, nu este necesar&#259; dac&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2074854608\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1764\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2074854608\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)fiecare dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nimplicate în fuziune a îndeplinit <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;ele</span> de\npublicitate a proiectului de fuziune prev&#259;zute de art. 242 cu cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o lun&#259; înainte ca fuziunea s&#259;\nproduc&#259; efecte;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_846465435\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1763\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_846465435\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)pe o perioad&#259; de o lun&#259; înaintea datei de la\ncare <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> produce efecte <span\nclass=SpellE>to&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante au putut consulta, la\nsediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> sau pe pagina web a\nacesteia, documentele prev&#259;zute la art. 244 alin. (1) lit. a), c) <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> d). <span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nart. 244 alin. (3)-(5) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1723659229\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1762\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1723659229\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)unul sau mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionari</span>/<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> ai <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante, <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inând</span>\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 5% din capitalul social subscris, au\nposibilitatea de a cere convocarea unei adun&#259;ri generale pentru a se <span\nclass=SpellE>pronun&#355;a</span> asupra fuziunii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_102850659\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1761\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_102850659\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul în care într-o fuziune prin <span class=SpellE>absorb&#355;ie</span>\nsocietatea absorbant&#259; <span class=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span> cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 90%, dar nu totalitatea <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>/<span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau a altor valori mobiliare ce\nconfer&#259; titularilor lor drept de vot în adun&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>,\naprobarea fuziunii de c&#259;tre adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nabsorbante nu este necesar&#259; dac&#259; sunt întrunite <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1). <span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> art.\n244 alin. (3)-(5) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>"}